-- Berkshire Hathaway gains at open as stock to be added to S&P 500
-- 
-- Fri Feb 12, 2010 9:40am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/02/12/us-markets-stocks-berkshire-idUSTRE61B2V820100212

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Berkshire Hathaway Inc ( BRKb.N ) shares gained at the open on Friday as investors were optimistic about the stock's coming addition to the S&P 500 index  .SPX  after the close. 

 The stock opened 0.7 percent higher at $77.22. (Reporting by  Angela Moon ; Editing by  James Dalgleish )